  m_Name: NeighborJournal_14
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 31
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #14 \u2014 C\u01B0 d\xE2n t\u1EA7ng 12"
  category: 3
  content: "Ng\xE0y 20 th\xE1ng 3. Ch\xFAng t\xF4i \u0111\xE3 barricade to\xE0n b\u1ED9
    t\u1EA7ng 12 t\u1EEB h\xF4m qua. Thang m\xE1y b\u1ECB c\u1EAFt, c\u1EEDa c\u1EA7u
    thang b\u1ECB ch\xE8n b\u1EB1ng t\u1EE7 l\u1EA1nh v\xE0 b\xE0n gh\u1EBF. C\xF3
    kho\u1EA3ng 15 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111ang tr\xFA \u1EA9n \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y. N\u01B0\u1EDBc
    v\xE0 \u0111\u1ED3 \u0103n ch\u1EC9 \u0111\u1EE7 cho 3 ng\xE0y n\u1EEFa. Ti\u1EBFng
    k\xEAu g\xE0o b\xEAn ngo\xE0i kh\xF4ng ng\u1EEBng. T\xF4i nh\xECn xu\u1ED1ng
    \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng th\u1EA5y qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i \u0111ang r\xFAt lui, b\u1ECF
    l\u1EA1i xe v\xE0 v\u0169 kh\xED. H\u1ECD c\u0169ng b\u1ECF ch\xFAng t\xF4i r\u1ED3i."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
